lead_paragraph: Florida State has had its share of struggles in Atlantic Coast Conference play. On Friday night, the Seminoles took advantage of Boston College's timely visit for their most-complete game of the season.

headline.print_headline: No. 20 Florida State Starts Fast in Rout of Boston College
